data.name: Jindriska, the Serene
data.notes: "Jindriska, the Serene" is in the ground on the southern ridge of Twin Arches, a pair of bridges and ridges in North West Oblivia. Twin Arches is too minor of an area to appear on the mini map but can be found near the mountain to the north west of Cliffside Camp. Check for the location name in the top right of the TV screen under Oblivia.
